{"id":152148,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/本拉登的秘密电邮系统/","date":"2011-05-13T22:17:48Z","modified":"2011-05-13T22:17:48Z","title":"本拉登的秘密电邮系统","content":"<p>美国海豹突击队在5月1日的行动中，从本拉登的藏身处缴获了大量硬盘和U盘等存储设备，美国情报官员正努力分析其中的邮件，破译出本拉登避开美国窃听的方法。 了解内情的匿名人士透露，虽然本拉登的藏身处没有互联网和电话接入，但他却是一位非常勤快的作者。他先在电脑上输入邮件内容，将其保存到U盘，交给一位信任的信使。信使再前往一个遥远的网吧，将U盘插入到电脑上，将本拉登的信息拷贝到一个电子邮件中，发送出去。本拉登接收信息的过程与之相反。信使先在网吧里拷贝下收件箱里的邮件，保存到U盘中，送到本拉登藏身处，供其阅读。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14d1e975/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%9C%AC%E6%8B%89%E7%99%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E7%94%B5%E9%82%AE%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F13%2F1429219%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%9C%AC%E6%8B%89%E7%99%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E7%94%B5%E9%82%AE%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F13%2F1429219%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092234348/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14d1e975/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092234348/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14d1e975/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=O27tkEAjE2Y:egFgD8qMZIA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=O27tkEAjE2Y:egFgD8qMZIA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[4643]}